      "rationale": "All five operating points were tested in three independent laboratories following ASTM F1841. Flow rate uncertainty ±0.05 L/min, rotational speed uncertainty ±10 RPM, fluid temperature ±0.3°C. Test condition documentation is complete and traceable to calibration records. Achieved level 4."
