      "rationale": "Quantitative E-metric comparison was performed for NIH at all five operating points. Velocity field comparison used qualitative contour overlays for three cross-sections; no scalar metric was applied to velocity fields. Achieved level 3 due to incomplete quantitative velocity comparison."
