      "rationale": "NIH is the direct clinical endpoint and was used as the primary QoI throughout. Global sensitivity analysis confirmed NIH is sensitive to the power-law exponent and inlet turbulence intensity. However, sub-lethal platelet activation index was not assessed as a secondary QoI despite its clinical relevance for VAD patients. Achieved level 4."
