      "rationale": "The SST k-omega turbulence model was selected based on literature review of rotating machinery benchmarks. Sensitivity to turbulence model was tested by comparing SST k-omega against realizable k-epsilon for one operating point; NIH differed by 18%. The Giersiepen-Wurzinger power-law hemolysis model was used without comparison to alternative formulations (e.g., Arora, Taskin). Model form uncertainty is inadequately characterized. Achieved level 3."
